		<title>EURGBP In Focus With PMI Data Release</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/en-au/analysis/market-news/eurgbp-focus-pmi-release</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 22 May 2025 01:09:04 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Market news & Insights]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[EURGBP]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.atfx.com/?p=50489</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[The EURGBP exchange rate has PMI data ahead on Thursday for the German and UK economies.  The EUR v GBP has slumped from 0.87 in April to 0.84 and is at risk of further losses with a weak bounce. The support level below is the 0.8323 figure.  Thursday’s data starts at 3:30pm HKT with the [&#8230;]]]></description>
